          <p class="light">Enter a keyword or twitter handle and get a fast summary of what people are saying.</p> </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="icon-block">
          <h2 class="center black-text"><i class="mdi-content-content-paste"></i></h2>
          <h5 class="center cyan-text text-darken-2">Analyze</h5>

          <p class="center black-text">Utilize Natural Language Processing to analyze and rate an overall sentiment for your searches</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="icon-block">
          <h2 class="center black-text"><i class="mdi-action-trending-up"></i></h2>
          <h5 class="center cyan-text text-darken-2">Track Trends</h5>

          <p class="center black-text text-darken-2">Schedule an automated email to track how a saved search is trending over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>



